      News story
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Improve a business with new skills: apply for funding
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Universities and research organisations can apply for a share of up to £10 million to work with businesses on solving their innovation challenges.</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
